English Translation

[Verse 1: Song Ji Eun]
It’s not love, this isn’t love
It’s just your obsession
Wherever I am, whatever I'm doing
It’s frightening, the way you watch me

[Verse 2: Bang Yong Guk]
I follow in your shadow, I call you
I become thrilled at the sound of your shaking breath
My heart runs after your increasingly quick steps
I think I’ll go crazy, the long night grows darker
Under the dead streetlamp in front of your house
I’m watching you through the crack in your window
Until the night ends, come on and find me
You keep playing a suffocating game
Of hide-and-seek with me

[Pre-Chorus: Bang Yong Guk]
You, you, you
You’re inseparable from me

[Chorus: Song Ji Eun]
Have you gone crazy?
Why are you like this?
Please just leave me alone now
Seeing you is suffocating
Please disappear from my sight

[Verse 3: Bang Yong Guk & Song Ji Eun]
You can never break away from me
You have no one to love but me
Try to escape, wherever you are
(I don’t wanna see you)
I can see you, you know deeply
You can never break away from me
You have no one to love but me
Look at me now
I don’t wanna cry no more, more

[Verse 4: Song Ji Eun]
Get lost
Just back off
I really can’t even breathe
Wherever I am, whatever I'm doing
It’s frightening, the way you follow me

[Verse 6: Bang Yong Guk]
A hundred times, tens of thousands of times
I've called you
But why, why is there no answer?
Did you forget?
It’s already been a thousand days since we met
I prepared a gift you’d like
I sit on the street you frequently travel
I’m waiting for you, I know my love
Don’t call it obsession
You don’t know love
Don’t say I’ve gone crazy
You don’t know my heart

[Pre-Chorus: Bang Yong Guk]
You, you, you
You’re inseparable from me

[Chorus: Song Ji Eun]
Have you gone crazy?
Why are you like this?
Please just leave me alone now
Seeing you is suffocating
Please disappear from my sight

[Bridge: Bang Yong Guk & Song Ji Eun]
You know you want me too
You know you love me
Don’t run away from me
Cut the crap
Get ahold of yourself and stop it
Let go of me now

[Outro: Song Ji Eun]
This ain’t right, This isn’t love
It’s just hurts me, don’t be like this
I loved you, But I don’t now
Erase me from your memory
I don’t wanna cry no more, more